          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The mechanism of the three-particle photonuclear",
                " reaction 7Li(gamma,p2t) MeV has been investigated at",
                " Eg < 27 MeV on the basis of the identified stars",
                " measured in nuclear emulsion.",
                "The formation of protons and two tritons in the",
                " reaction is explained using the feynman diagram",
                " mechanism with the virtual cluster (n-6Li) or (p-6He)",
                " states of 7Li nucleus. The gamma-quantum absorption by",
                " the a=6 cluster with disintegration into two A=3",
                " fragments, and rescattering of virtual nucleon at the",
                " A=3 nucleus with formation of final particles is taken",
                " into consideration.  To identify the mechanism of the",
                " simplest feynman diagrams the usage of correlations",
                " between the energies of incident and emitting",
                " particles in virtual processes was suggested."
              ]
            }
          ],
